  "title": "Fiery Island Flower",
  "secondName": "Fiery Island Flower",
  "description": "Sitting by the pool with flowers in her hair and a picnic basket at her side, Antares may seem like a natural at this 'vacation' thing. But don't be fooled. Relaxing is harder than it looks.\n\nLaomis has lived up to its reputation as a paradise. Everywhere she looks, there's another view to appreciate, another meal to try, another kind local to meet...she can barely keep up with it all! How will she ever experience the whole island before the season ends?\n\nOh. That's right: summer will come again soon. Maybe, bit by bit, year by year, she can become a vacation master after all.",
